title: Sydney Scott Jean-The Incidental Man
description:
Superhero or supervillain? Dan has a useless superpower. Plagued by accidents that are beyond his control, he retreats from life. However, his best friend Sarah convinces him that if he is honest and warns people about his affliction, then they would have the ability to make their own informed choice of whether to stick around. Taking her advice, he comes out of hiding and pursues a normal life, one that includes a job, a house and even a wife.

However, it becomes apparent that he is just making up the rules as he goes along, and as his power inflicts chaos on the unsuspecting world, his poor enduring wife Cassie, hurt time and time again, desperately begins to search for a way out
